	column 'Has Hours Since Estimate' = ```
			
			IF(
			    'Job'[Job Status] = "Active" || 
			    CALCULATE([Hours Actual, Est to Date]) > 0,
			    TRUE(),
			    FALSE()
			)
			```
		formatString: """TRUE"";""TRUE"";""FALSE"""
